                    <supplied reason="subaudible">and in</supplied>
                    the temple <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kōyil</foreign></supplied> of Vīra Murukki<note>That is, Murukku.</note> Nāṅkai
                    ...
                    a pillar <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tirunilai</foreign></supplied> of the <foreign>maṇḍapa</foreign> built by ... Paṇṭitar ...</p>
